item.title: Need help creating my dope server
item.dc:creator: @mista_pnut mista pnut
item.description:
@mista_pnut wrote:

No, we’re not being dicks, we’re just tired of our help section being full of these types of topics forcing people’s topics that actually need help to be forced down and never seen.

Rule number one of the Server Help section reads:

1. All topics in this section must be requests for help on a server. Any non-server related questions will be locked. Requesting a host, [b]'coder'/programmer[/b], server or client, or asking about a VPS also falls under being non-server related. That means for other sections on this site too.

If you believe that you would like to make a development team we have specific sections for that, but nobody is going to make a server for you.
